"Sab Thik Chal rha tha,
Najaane fir kya baat hogayi,
Hawa ka ek jhoka aaya,
aur bin mausam barsaat ho gayi,
zindagi yun badal gayi,
meri aankh jhapakte hi,
khushi me din guzra,
aur gam bhari raat ho gayi."

"Socha tumhare liye tadapna,
chhod denge......
Socha tumhare liye tarasna, 
chhod denge..........
Dil se kaha ae dil bhul ja usse....
Dil ne kaha dobara kaha toh,
Dhadakna chhod denge...."

"Tha koi mera jo mere dil ko jhakam de gaya
Zindagi bhar rone ki kasam de gaya
Laakho phulo me ek chuna tha
jo kaanto se bhi gehra Zakham de gaya..!!"

"Mil jaaye sab kuch jindagi mein,
Toh fariyad kiski karoge,
Mulaqat hone lage jo roz roz
Toh yaad kise karoge"
